<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>DieWhenYouDie2026</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            /*justify-content: center;*/
            /*text-align: center; */
            flex-direction: column;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        #container {
            padding: 2vh;
            font-size: 2vh;
        }

        #content {
            padding-top: 5vh;
        }

        #bottom {
            animation: skull-drop 3s ease forwards;
            animation-delay: 3s;
        }


        .first-letter {
            font-size: 2em;
        }

        .capitalized {
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .title {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1em;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        img {
            height: 10vh;
           
        }

        #skull {
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            top: 0px;
            /* center horizontally using transform (translate is not a valid CSS property) */
            transform: translate(-50%, 0);
            opacity: 0;
            font-size: 1vh;
            pointer-events: none;
            animation: skull-drop 3s ease forwards;
            animation-delay: 3s;
        }



        @keyframes skull-drop {
            0% {
                transform: translate(0, -100vh);
                opacity: 0;
            }

            80% {
                opacity: 1;
            }

            100% {
                transform: translate(0, 0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="container">
        <div id="content">
            <p><span class="first-letter">W</span>hy is existence so painful?</p>
            <p>Couldn't I just be put away and stored. Forgotten and Silent</p>
            <p>Like a pack of Ramen noodles that fell behind the fridge</p>
            <br>

            ---------------

            <p><span class="first-letter">E</span>very day filled with thinking and feeling and hurting
            <p>

            <p>Life is <span class="capitalized">Relentless</span> </p>
            ---------------
            <p><span class="first-letter">D</span>ear <span class="capitalized">Mictlāntēcutli</span> ...please make it
                stop
            </p>
            <p>Looking forward to the great escape. That glorious sleep</p>
            <p>Death will embrace us as we sigh with relief</p>
            <br>

        </div>

        <div id="bottom">

            <p class="title">DieWhenYouDie 2026</p>
            <p class="subtitle">November 7</p>
            <br>

            <img src="dist/img/mict.png" alt="Skull">
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>